english.verse1: Dashing through the snow In a one-horse open sleigh. O'er the fields we go. Laughing all the way. Bells on bobtails ring. Making spirits bright. What fun it is to ride and sing. A sleighing song tonight.
english.chorus: Jingle bells, jingle bells. Jingle all the way. Oh, what fun it is to ride. In a one-horse open sleigh, hey. Jingle bells, jingle bells. Jingle all the way. Oh, what fun it is to ride. In a one-horse open sleigh.
